#18

Brambleton Golf Course

42180 Ryan Rd

Ashburn, VA 20148-6920, United States

703.327.3403

Brambleton Golf Course is a public course owned and operated by the Northern Virginia Regional Park Authority, and located in a well-wooded part of Loudoun County.

The standard walking rates are $35 Mondays through Thursdays, then $47 on Fridays, weekends, and holidays (carts are $16/person).
